<h2 id="use-consistent-and-meaningful-naming-scheme">use consistent and meaningful naming scheme</h2>

<p>donâ€™t confuse your future self</p>

<h2 id="keep-code-and-data-separate">keep code and data separate</h2>

<pre><code>/code
/data
